data.description: Discover a luxurious lifestyle in this fully furnished two-bedroom villa, complete with a versatile den and two baths, all overlooking a serene lake. With a spacious primary bedroom, a modern kitchen and private screened lanai, this a wonderful place to retreat. Naples Reserve offers top-notch amenities, from a resort-style pool and fitness center to pickleball courts and boating available on the larger lake by the clubhouse. Located with easy access to downtown Naples, as well as the beautiful beaches in Marco Island.
